</div>
<div class="bg-stone-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
        <div class="w-full mx-auto font-barlow h-72 bg-[url('/static/img/r-kinantan.png')] bg-right bg-contain bg-no-repeat rounded-md shadow">
            <div class="relative w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-blue-700/70 rounded-md text-white/90 text-xl font-barlow p-8 pr-48 text-justify">
                <p class="text-justify">
                    soal yang tersedia di CPC COMPFEST bagus dan menantang,
                    terutama beberapa soal pada babak final. Salah satu soal
                    final mengajarkanku cara pandang dan cara manipulasi baru
                    dari suatu topik advanced di competitive programming. Saya
                    lihat keseluruhan COMPFEST terlaksana secara profesional dan
                    cukup well-prepared
                </p>
                <p class="absolute text-right right-24 bottom-8 font-bold">
                    Kinantan Arya Bagaspati
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-stone-200">
    <h1 class="text-center text-5xl font-barlow-semi italic font-black py-12">FAQ</h1>
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pb-12 space-y-2">
        <div class="bg-stone-300 rounded shadow font-barlow" x-data="{ disclosed: false }">
            <div @click="disclosed = !disclosed" class="p-3">
                <h3>Kapan hari terakhir pendaftaran?</h3>
            </div>
            <div  class="px-4 pb-4" x-show="disclosed" x-collapse>
                <hr class="pt-4 border-stone-500 border-1"/>
                Sabtu, 17 September 2022
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-300 rounded shadow font-barlow" x-data="{ disclosed: false }">
            <div @click="disclosed = !disclosed" class="p-3">
                <h3>Bolehkah satu tim untuk seorang aja?</h3>
            </div>
            <div  class="px-4 pb-4" x-show="disclosed" x-collapse>
                <hr class="pt-4 border-stone-500 border-1"/>
                Boleh dong!
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-300 rounded shadow font-barlow" x-data="{ disclosed: false }">
            <div @click="disclosed = !disclosed" class="p-3">
                <h3>Berapa biaya pendaftaran?</h3>
            </div>
            <div  class="px-4 pb-4" x-show="disclosed" x-collapse>
                <hr class="pt-4 border-stone-500 border-1"/>
                Early (20 Agustus - 31 Agustus 2022) : Rp 125.000,00 - per tim, Regular (1 September - 17 September 2022) : Rp 150.000,00 - per tim
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-300 rounded shadow font-barlow" x-data="{ disclosed: false }">
            <div @click="disclosed = !disclosed" class="p-3">
                <h3>Dimana bisa akses soal P1?</h3>
            </div>
            <div  class="px-4 pb-4" x-show="disclosed" x-collapse>
                <hr class="pt-4 border-stone-500 border-1"/>
                Daftar dan bayar dulu lalu submit ke google form. Baru email yang berisi file soal (untuk bidang IPA) atau link google form soal (untuk bidang mat) akan dikirimkan ke email peserta yang didaftarkan
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-300 rounded shadow font-barlow" x-data="{ disclosed: false }">
            <div @click="disclosed = !disclosed" class="p-3">
                <h3>Berapa banyak tim yang akan lolos dari penyisihan 2 ke semifinal?</h3>
            </div>
            <div  class="px-4 pb-4" x-show="disclosed" x-collapse>
                <hr class="pt-4 border-stone-500 border-1"/>
                Hanya 15 tim.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-300 rounded shadow font-barlow" x-data="{ disclosed: false }">
            <div @click="disclosed = !disclosed" class="p-3">
                <h3>Berapa banyak tim yang akan lolos dari semifinal ke final?</h3>
            </div>
            <div  class="px-4 pb-4" x-show="disclosed" x-collapse>
                <hr class="pt-4 border-stone-500 border-1"/>
                Hanya 6 tim.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-300 rounded shadow font-barlow" x-data="{ disclosed: false }">
            <div @click="disclosed = !disclosed" class="p-3">
                <h3>Apa format Brilliant Competition tahun ini?</h3>
            </div>
            <div  class="px-4 pb-4" x-show="disclosed" x-collapse>
                <hr class="pt-4 border-stone-500 border-1"/>
                Brilliant Competition akan mengadakan 2 perlombaan tim, yaitu lomba matematika dan lomba IPA, dengan tiap tim terdiri dari sebanyak 2 orang
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-300 rounded shadow font-barlow" x-data="{ disclosed: false }">
            <div @click="disclosed = !disclosed" class="p-3">
                <h3>Apakah ada silabus untuk Brilliant Competition tahun ini?</h3>
            </div>
            <div  class="px-4 pb-4" x-show="disclosed" x-collapse>
                <hr class="pt-4 border-stone-500 border-1"/>
                Silabus Bcomp terdapat diatas, untuk IPA berkisar materi OSN SMP
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-stone-600">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 px-4 mx-auto font-barlow">
            <a href="/about-us" class="p-5 border rounded border-gray-200 hover:bg-white/10 text-white">
                <h3>Learn more about us →</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
